html:
There is a schedule here
A new schedule again
Just one of schedules
But not one of mine
Is everything ok
Nagging
I have to deal with it
Can't do nothing about it
The doc is juggling pills
In a bright room
Full of medicaments
A worker is looking silently
Last days of vacations
In a broom depiosit
And I'm still young
Still I have life ahead
title: Broom deposite
